'''多溴二苯醚'''（{{lang-en|Polybrominated diphenyl ethers}}，缩写'''PBDEs'''）是一类[[有机溴化合物|有机溴化合物]]，常用作[[阻燃剂|阻燃剂]]。和其它[[有机溴阻燃剂|有机溴阻燃剂]]类似，多溴二苯醚已被广泛用于各种产品的防火，包括建筑材料、电子产品、家具、塑料、[[聚氨酯|聚氨酯]]泡沫、纺织品等<ref>{{cite journal | pmc = 3113369 | pmid=21591615 | doi=10.1021/es2007462 | volume=45 | issue=12 | title=Identification of flame retardants in polyurethane foam collected from baby products | year=2011 | journal=Environ. Sci. Technol. | pages=5323–31 |vauthors=Stapleton HM, Klosterhaus S, Keller A, Ferguson PL, van Bergen S, Cooper E, Webster TF, Blum A | bibcode=2011EnST...45.5323S }}</ref>。多溴二苯醚在结构上类似于[[多氯联苯|多氯联苯]]（PCBs）等[[多鹵代化合物|多鹵代化合物]]，同时也是一种[[持久性有機污染物|持久性有機污染物]]（POPs）<ref>{{Cite journal| doi = 10.1289/ehp.0901450| pmid = 20103495| year = 2010| last1 = Harley | first1 = K.| last2 = Marks | first2 = A.| last3 = Chevrier | first3 = J.| last4 = Bradman | first4 = A.| last5 = Sjödin | first5 = A.| last6 = Eskenazi | first6 = B.| title = PBDE Concentrations in Women's Serum and Fecundability.| journal = Environmental Health Perspectives| volume = 118| issue = 5| pages = 699–704| pmc = 2866688 }}</ref>。

